system.conkyrc:
 System Information
 * Disk info
 * Networking (wireless, wired, vpn)
 * Top Programs

main.conkyrc:
 Statusbar like information
 * cpu,mem,disk io, bandwidth, updates, battery, mail
 NOTE: Change PATH_TO_YOUR_MAIL to your maildir

I also have a calendar/pim conkyrc. See http://blog.stebalien.com/2010/05/turn-zim-desktop-wiki-into-calendar.html
